name: Kahuna
description: Kahuna is a 4-way cross between Super Skunk, Big Skunk Korean, Jack Herer, and Afghan Hawaiian that brings together a wide set of influences for a complex high. The Kahuna variety has both tropical influences in its parentage and spiritually attuning effects when used.
